headline: Is It Time To Reconsider Accenture (ACN) After Its Recent Share Price Pullback?
summary: If you are wondering whether Accenture's current share price lines up with its underlying worth, you are not alone. That is exactly what this article is set up to unpack. Accenture last closed at US$281.82, with returns of 5.0% over the past 7 days, 4.6% over 30 days, 8.4% year to date and a 19.6% decline over the past year. These figures can change how investors think about both upside potential and risk. Recent headlines around consulting demand, artificial intelligence related services...
